com.versant.odmg
Interface Collection

All Known Subinterfaces:
Bag, List, Set
public interface Collection

ODMG 2.0 Java binding defines the Collection Interface. The Bag, List, and Set Interfaces extend the Collection Interface. The Collection elements are of type object. You must convert subclasses of object, such as class Employee, when you use them as Collection elements. (Java converts them automatically on insertion in a collection, but requires an explicit cast when retrieved).
